Building
========

In order to build this code, you need golang to be installed
on your system.

To install go, see: https://golang.org/doc/install#install

After that, just `cd` into this folder and run:

```
make
```

to fetch the necessary libs and tools and to generate the lexer.

----------------------------------------------------------------

Running
=======

The lexer can be run after generating as follows:

```
bin/lexer test/test1.go
```
